Class BaseDefinitionMetaTagNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.common.SourceLocation
      • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.tree.as.NodeBase

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDecoration, IMetaInfo, ISourceLocation, IASNode, IDefinitionNode, IDocumentableDefinitionNode, IMetaTagNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EffectTagNode, EventTagNode, StyleTagNode

    public abstract class BaseDefinitionMetaTagNode
extends MetaTagNode
implements IDefinitionNode, IDocumentableDefinitionNode
    For metatags that decorate a definition, such as Events, Effects and Styles, we treat them internally as IDefinitions. This is the common baseclass for all of them
